GO
CREATE PROC [dbo].[ImportFactRentals] AS begin

insert into dbo.FactRentals
(
	TransactionID
	, CustomerSK
	, LocationSK
	, MovieSK
	, RentalDateSK
	, ReturnDateSK
	, RentalDuration
	, RentalCost
	, LateFee
	, TotalCost
	, RewindFlag
)
select
	r.SourceSystemTransactionID as TransactionID
	, c.CustomerSK
	, r.SourceSystemId
	, m.MovieSK
	, rent.DateSK
	, ret.DateSK
	, datediff(day, r.RentalDate, r.ReturnDate) + 1 as RentalDuration
	, r.RentalCost
	, r.LateFee
	, r.RentalCost + r.LateFee as TotalCost
	, r.RewindFlag
from extern.rentals r
inner join dbo.DimCustomers c on c.CustomerID = r.CustomerID
inner join dbo.DimMovies m on m.MovieID = r.MovieID
inner join dbo.DimDate as rent on rent.DateValue = r.RentalDate
left outer join dbo.DimDate as ret on ret.DateValue = r.ReturnDate
where
	not exists (select 1 from dbo.FactRentals f where f.TransactionID = r.SourceSystemTransactionID)

END
GO
